                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-52-defend552 t18000528-52-punish294"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the first Middilesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
